title: MisterMusic Show 415 - indie, alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 415 - 192kbps MP3  [120 min] -



New music this week from The Boxer Rebellion, Red Hot Chili Peppers, and Pete Yorn on the show.  The 'Oldie of the Week' was a number 1 alternative rock hit for 3 weeks during July 1996.
Plus the usual mix of indie, alternative, and classic hits from over 5 decades.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page-  
http://mistermusicshow.com/ . Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search mistermusicshow (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

to enjoy in the hectic schedules of today. Check it out- PodCloud1 'The One for Great Music' http://podcloud1.com/
